<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>设置绑定邮箱</title>
    <link href="../fontAwesome/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css"/>
    <style>
        body{
            background-color: #f5f6f8;
        }
        .hmenu{
            width: 80%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px #ccc;
            background-color: #f5f6f8;
        }

        .index{
            color:#777;
        }
        .index:hover{
            color:#ED7612;
        }
        .breadcrumb{
            text-align: left;
            background-color: #f5f6f8;
        }
        .breadcrumb > li + li:before {
            color:#333;
            content: ">\00a0";
        }
        ol li{
            font-size: small;
            font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color:#333;
        }
        .hmain{
            line-height:1.5em;
        }
        .form-group{
               margin-top: 2em;
           }
        .panel{
            margin-top: -1.5em;
            box-shadow: 1px 1px 1px 1px #999;

        }
        .panel-heading{
            background-color: #f9f9f9;

        }
        .panel-title{
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 0.5em;
        }

        /*下划线*/
        .panel-title a{
            text-decoration: none;
            border-bottom: solid 2px #ED7612;
            display: block;
            padding-bottom: 1em;
            width: 10em;
        }
        .hbound{
            padding-left: 2em;
        }

        label{
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #333;
        }
        .himg{
           height: 5em;
            margin-top: 2em;
        }
        #bemailcode{
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        #authcodeImg{
            /*width: 7em;*/
            height: 2.5em;
            vertical-align: middle;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color:aquamarine;
        }
        #change_authcode{
            position: relative;
            top: 0.5em;
        }
        #bestepbtn{
            margin-top: 1em;
            width: 10em;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 900;
        }
      #bestepbtn:focus,#bestepbtn_back:focus{
            outline:0;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: myfont;
            src:url('./fontAwesome/font/VINERITC.TTF');
        }
        .hwhy{
            margin-top: 3em;
            margin-left: 8em;
            font-size: 12px;
            color:#666;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .hwhy>p:first-child{
            font-size: 14px;
            color:#333;
        }
        .hwhy>a{
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .panel-footer{
            border-top: 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="row hmenu">
    <div class="hmain col-md-offset-3 col-md-9">
        <div class="row ">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
                <li><strong style="color:#ED7612">|</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="#" class="index">我的书来熟往</a></li>
                <li class="active">设置绑定邮箱</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#"><div class="hbound">设置绑定邮箱</div></a></h4>
            </div>

            <div class="panel-body">

                <div id="bestepone">
                    <div class="row himg">
                        <img src="../img/img_h/estep1.png"/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row" style="text-align: center;">
                        <form action="#" method="post" class="form-horizontal">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class=" col-md-offset-2 col-md-3 control-label">验证邮箱：</label>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="bemail" placeholder="请输入邮箱" required="required">
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-3 control-label">验证码：</label>
                                <div class="input-group">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="bemailcode" placeholder="请输入验证码">
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="authcodeImg" class="col-md-3">d4fw</div>
                                    <a href="javascript:" id="change_authcode">换一张</a>
                                </div>

                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group">
                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning" id="bestepbtn">下一步</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <div id="besteptwo">
                    <div class="row himg">
                        <img src="../img/img_h/estep2.png"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row" style="text-align: center;margin-top: 3em">
                        <p>恭喜您，您的邮箱已绑定成功！</p>
                        <p> <a href="#"><button type="button" class="btn btn-link" id="bestepbtn_back">返回</button></a>
                           继续完善个人资料
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>
            <div class="panel-footer">
                <div class="row hwhy">
                    <p>为什么验证邮箱？</p>
                    <p>1.验证邮箱可加强账户安全，您可以使用已验证的邮箱快速找回密码或支付密码。</p>
                    <p>2.如验证邮箱遇到问题？请<a href="#">联系客服。</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="../js/static/jquery-2.2.2.min.js"></script>
<script src="../bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
    $(function (){
        $('#bestepone').show();
        $('#besteptwo').hide();
        $('#bestepbtn').click(function(){
            $('#bestepone').hide();
            $('#besteptwo').show();
        })
    })

</script>
</body>
</html>